  "text": "The Lie bracket computation can be found in a paper by Crouch [CITATION_1] , where the author proves a basically equivalent result to Proposition 4.2, namely the complete controllability of system (A, Π) in the case γ = 0 (T free), under the assumption that the set of admissible controls is a bounded rectangle.",
